{"tid":1248148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英文文宣】【copypasta】資料齊全！向外國人解釋送中條例以及黑警暴力","createTime":"2019-06-21T11:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T22:42:31.000Z","uid":138409,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"180c037966daa3799b64bcdc2c75ef6fe13ee50c","tid":1248148,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"大家可以copy低<br />\n然後去各大英文媒體留言區洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nHi there,<br />\n<br />\nThis article is quite accurate in describing the current political turmoil in Hong Kong. If you want to know more, scroll down for info.<br />\n<br />\nFurther reading:<br />\n<br />\n1.Local backlashes<br />\n<br />\nThe following website sums up the reasons why Hongkongers found the extradition bill revolting.<br />\n<a href=\"https://beta.hackfoldr.org/extradition/https%253A%252F%252Fextradition.g0vhk.io%252F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta.hackfoldr.org%2Fextradition%2Fhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fextradition.g0vhk.io%25252F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=900243ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beta.hackfoldr.org/extradition/https%253A%252F%252Fextradition.g0vhk.io%252F</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Bar Association has also voiced out against this piece of legislation<br />\nBrief guide<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Ip6QLD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ip6QLD&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=728eeb33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Ip6QLD</a><br />\n<br />\nObservations <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IFOPdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IFOPdU&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=c98fddcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IFOPdU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WD2gU7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WD2gU7&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=ef2be699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WD2gU7</a><br />\n<br />\n2.International criticisms<br />\nNumerous legal associations have jointly issued an opinion piece, criticising the extradition bill as  &rdquo;ill-conceived proposals&rdquo; that &ldquo;fundamentally imperil the operation of the rule of law in<br />\nHong Kong.&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fairtrials.org/sites/default/files/publication_pdf/Joint-observations-human-rights-implications-Hong-Kong-Fugitive-Offenders-Mutual-Legal-Assistance-Criminal-Matters-Legislation.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fairtrials.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpublication_pdf%2FJoint-observations-human-rights-implications-Hong-Kong-Fugitive-Offenders-Mutual-Legal-Assistance-Criminal-Matters-Legislation.pdf&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=3df9bdc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fairtrials.org/sites/default/files/publication_pdf/Joint-observations-human-rights-implications-Hong-Kong-Fugitive-Offenders-Mutual-Legal-Assistance-Criminal-Matters-Legislation.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3.Police brutality<br />\n<br />\nAmnesty International recently published a report, stating that during the protest on June 12th, &ldquo;the use of force by police in the largely peaceful protest was unnecessary and excessive. The use of force during the protest violated international human rights law and standards.&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/asa17/0576/2019/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fasa17%2F0576%2F2019%2Fen%2F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=1d7f15ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/asa17/0576/2019/en/</a> <br />\n<br />\nVerified footages corresponding to their locations available in this interactive map<br />\n<a href=\"https://story.mapme.com/5f0f348c-8af8-44e5-bfa6-4c55de1bbec0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstory.mapme.com%2F5f0f348c-8af8-44e5-bfa6-4c55de1bbec0&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=462f9a95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://story.mapme.com/5f0f348c-8af8-44e5-bfa6-4c55de1bbec0</a><br />\n<br />\nMore footages:<br />\n<a href=\"https://elab.hker.tech/1TKFgCjzW5XTcIIRcu1gg_WK4BsQADHOz5lJHPXGsPc4/https%253A%252F%252Fethercalc.org%252Felabpolice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felab.hker.tech%2F1TKFgCjzW5XTcIIRcu1gg_WK4BsQADHOz5lJHPXGsPc4%2Fhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fethercalc.org%25252Felabpolice&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDciBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=eb7a7272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://elab.hker.tech/1TKFgCjzW5XTcIIRcu1gg_WK4BsQADHOz5lJHPXGsPc4/https%253A%252F%252Fethercalc.org%252Felabpolice</a><br />\n<br />\n4. Our goals<br />\nWe Hongkongers will not yield until the regime satisfies our 5 demands:<br />\n&mdash; Fully withdraw (instead of &ldquo;postponing&rdquo;) the extradition bill<br />\n&mdash; Retract the official characterisation of the June12th protest as &ldquo;riot&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Release all arrested protesters and promise that they won&rsquo;t be prosecuted in the future<br />\n&mdash; Make police liable for their brutality<br />\n&mdash; Resignation of HK chief executive, Carrie Lam<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention<br />\n<br />\nBest wishes,<br />\nA HongKonger"},{"pid":"fff0031e9f717c86b1860d310b767b3b307f9aa8","tid":1248148,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e6e6da40bae66486d558565a3646a13d8a12c39","tid":1248148,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/